Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.34,0:01:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分開了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、火美子和武一郎師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.05,0:01:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊在各界層\N與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊以第七界層為目標進發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.32,0:01:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上到第三界層的我們\N知道了這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.71,0:01:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為極寒之劍和灼熱之劍\N交換了的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.70,0:01:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令這裏變成了灼熱地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要令這裏恢復原狀\N便要找出極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們得知了它在第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.17,0:02:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我便一個人上到了第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.12,0:02:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當終於找出了極寒之劍時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.82,0:02:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我眼前出現了\N因為古拿瑪出賣的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.13,0:02:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而被捉的火美子和武一郎師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十八話\N熱啊熱啊,飛走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搖啊!搖啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.00,0:02:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要怎樣做?小鬼\N如果你拔出那把極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.65,0:02:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們便會死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.62,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道救世主會捨棄同伴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.51,0:02:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真卑鄙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.46,0:03:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,不要理在下了\N喂!那裏的呆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.64,0:03:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呆子?難道是叫我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了你還有誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.64,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下怎樣也無所謂\N但是請你放過火美子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,放我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.37,0:03:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…\N才不是會聽這種話的人物!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.03,0:03:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師、火美子\N放心吧,我來救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是來救我的嗎?\N為…為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?\N我們不是同伴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同伴…同伴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同…同伴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?你剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.16,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我請求你停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,你說要求我嗎?\N好,我停手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要你用手指\N插入鼻孔轉三個圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再高呼所也所也大人萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.79,0:04:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想的話 ,不干也可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,我干便是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.69,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也大人萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樣子好古怪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要幹得高興點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也大人萬歲!\N太小聲了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太沒出息了,渡!\N你這樣也算是在下的徒弟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.09,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,夠了,渡\N在下已經早有覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.68,0:05:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了世界,為了世人而死\N是武士的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.82,0:05:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,是身為男人的本份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算這個身體燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈魂也會\N成為天空上燦爛的的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.73,0:05:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直地…一直地守護著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師…師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.72,0:05:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.22,0:05:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔兵,點火!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是不想死\N不要!不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個呢,大叔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不要,還是不要\N在下還有很多東西想吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.57,0:06:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有山珍海味,鮑參翅肚\N我還是不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點點火吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒豬!燒豬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎辦好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.93,0:06:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,我覺得很熱我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個小鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙…\N他來幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那部魔神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.96,0:07:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,擊比倫部隊\N不要給他們逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.67,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的子彈打不中的\N喂,你不反擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是說得輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不會有事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題,一定可以順利逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也要快點拔出極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.12,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?\N要射準一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愉快,愉快\N差不多是時候走了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩!要撞了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.45,0:08:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!可惡的古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也,去追擊他們\N絕對不能讓他們逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.04,0:08:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們三個上第四界層\N去收拾那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼拔不出來啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點的話\N師傅和火美子會很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉,請你放手啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話就算破壞胡娜拉像\N也要把劍取去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.97,0:08:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,走開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.94,0:09:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手,胡娜拉\N求求你幫助渡吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你,請你把劍交給渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡取劍不是用來做壞事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.07,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了救自己的同伴\N和創界山的眾生用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.97,0:09:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我求你\N請你把劍交給渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.75,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉像在哭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她把劍放開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.55,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!\N終於把極寒之劍取到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉,謝謝你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是胡娜拉的眼淚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得很好,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.82,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,你看\N這是極寒之劍啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.73,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次你幹得很了不起\N但不可以只顧高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點回去第三界層不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢,我很擔心大家\N走吧,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.97,0:10:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉像替我們開路了\N我們跳進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.66,0:10:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!雪,你和西蒙一起\N在千人僊人那處等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次我會把灼熱之劍帶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.47,0:11:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心了,渡\N我一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛!在下的背燒傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真煩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然救了他們\N我到底在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.60,0:11:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我已不能再變回原狀了\N不只這樣,連性命也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.34,0:11:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…對了\N現在在這裏解決了他們的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.09,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨!在危險的時候\N讓你救了我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖不知你是誰\N可以讓我們見一見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!請等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做不到…要殺他們我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.25,0:12:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃到哪裏也沒用\N你只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪…\N鳥先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是古拿瑪駕駛那魔神的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活該,我會替你作墓的你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在此之前要先收拾你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也,今次的對手是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你回來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!\N他逃過了殘酷大人的追殺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,把你們一起收拾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做得到嗎?\N龍神丸,用炎龍拳吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什麼,反炎龍拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的,龍神丸\N你的招式我們已全部研究過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.84,0:13:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧!必殺性感熱吻火炎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.13,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可怕的高溫火炎\N中了這招便完了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.16,0:13:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N對方是什麼也能溶掉的高熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們用什麼也能冰封的寒氣\N決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.89,0:13:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸\N我把極寒之劍的力量傳給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,試試吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.81,0:14:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的廢劍有什麼用?\N用這收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.66,0:14:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性感熱吻火炎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.06,0:14:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N就這樣還給他吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極寒登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超級屈辱啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.77,0:14:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,我一開始便是為了\N當間諜才成為你們的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此已沒什麼好說了\N隨便你們處置吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪是…多惡達的手下?\N你騙人吧?古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,在下還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.59,0:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在熱島被捉,是這傢伙佈局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼會呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部鳥形魔神\N便是最有力的證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.85,0:15:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,不要啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.28,0:15:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就如你所願\N把你的頭砍下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.54,0:15:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確騙了你們\N來吧,因為我是間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.63,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,你好像已經覺悟了\N這樣的話…我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.39,0:15:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你們幹什麼?\N不要啊,快放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和火美子險些便被燒死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.54,0:15:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是古拿瑪不是來救你了嗎\N師傅,可以殺救命恩人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生是好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.51,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是這樣,至今為止\N我們遇上了多少危險的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…\N那一定是有什麼理由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高興,渡,很多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過算了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.35,0:16:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能被你們喚做同伴已足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.56,0:16:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我已留下回憶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,快來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.53,0:16:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老…老師!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的一劍\N已把以前的古拿瑪殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永別了,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的淚水\N是從你的真心流出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要活著便定會有好事發生\N好好生存吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!\N鳥先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,用極寒之劍吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉\N請你賜力量給極寒之劍吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個便是亞撒姆像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,你幫幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.26,0:17:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,讓我騎上你的背吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.06,0:18:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞撒姆\N我是來把極寒之劍還給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把灼熱之劍交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放回了,放回了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.76,0:18:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼放回了極寒之劍\N火炎也沒有熄滅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底…\N啊!出路消失了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去的話\N我們會被燒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.06,0:18:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?亞撒姆\N為什麼火炎不熄滅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.50,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.36,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你為什麼來這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算把極寒之劍放回\N也不能令這世界復原的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.11,0:19:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.34,0:19:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為多惡達\N把灼熱之盾的龍之眼取走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.93,0:19:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍之眼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.76,0:19:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有龍之眼\N也不能令這灼熱地獄平息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.03,0:19:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,已來到這裏\N竟也沒有辦法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.78,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要氣妥,渡\N你冷靜地想想,會有辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是胡娜拉給我的胡娜拉之淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.12,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是胡娜拉和亞撒姆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.30,0:21:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彩虹啊\N又一條彩虹恢復原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?老公公…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.09,0:21:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又去了哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塗啊塗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛…你再輕力一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.39,0:21:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是有古拿瑪\N便不能令第三界層恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生,我很喜歡你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你們,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!古拿瑪你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知為何\N突然很想向著夕陽奔走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.55,0:21:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"夥伴"真是好東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.99,0:22:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!今次是第四界層了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.95,0:22:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!

